headline: Delisting of Securities from The Nasdaq Stock Market
summary: NEW YORK, Aug. 05, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- The Nasdaq Stock Market announced today that it will delist the American depositary shares of Secoo Holding Limited. Secoo Holding Limited’s security was suspended on April 26, 2024 and has not traded on Nasdaq since that time. Nasdaq also announced today that it will delist the common stock of PaxMedica, Inc.
